'''聖陶利髮型'''（{{lang-en|Centauri hairtyle}}）是一種[[髮型|髮型]]，頭髮像[[孔雀|孔雀]]開屏一樣在[[冠狀面|冠狀面]]上向外發散，類似轉了九十度的[[莫霍克髮型|莫霍克髮型]]，也有人用[[日出|日出]]來描述此髮型<ref name=JMS/>。這種髮型源自科幻影集《[[巴比倫五號|巴比倫五號]]》中的虛構的[[外星人|外星人]]聖陶利人。

==巴比倫五號==

在《巴比倫五號》影集中，大多數聖陶利男性都是這種髮型，頭髮的長度和[[男子氣概|男子氣概]]或[[社會地位|社會地位]]有關<ref>{{cite web|title=Londo Mollari and the Centauri Republic|author=J. Michael Straczynski|date=1995-10-08|publisher=The Lurker's Guide to Babylon 5|url=http://www.midwinter.com/lurk/chars/londo.html|accessdate=2020-07-22|archive-date=2020-08-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200803060815/http://www.midwinter.com/lurk/chars/londo.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

在影集原本的[[概念藝術|概念圖]]中，聖陶利人的髮型是整齊地向後梳，後面略高。化妝部門準備了像孔雀開屏的[[假髮|假髮]]，準備剪短後梳成概念圖中的造形，然而在第一次上妝時，演員{{le|彼德．朱拉西科|Peter Jurasik}}戴著未處理好的假髮，向製作人[[約瑟夫·麥可·斯特拉日恩斯基|斯特拉日恩斯基]]開玩笑說他覺得這樣的造型很棒，而斯特拉日恩斯基未意識到朱拉西科是在開玩笑，決定尊重演員的專業判斷，造成此髮型成為影集中的聖陶利人標準造形，朱拉西科接下來五年都必須以這樣的角色造形出場。<ref name=JMS>{{cite web|title=J Michael Straczynski的訪問|publisher=Television Academy Foundation|url=https://interviews.televisionacademy.com/interviews/j-michael-straczynski|accessdate=2020-07-22|archive-date=2020-08-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200801012537/https://interviews.televisionacademy.com/interviews/j-michael-straczynski|dead-url=no}}</ref>

這種髮型後來成為朱拉西科的角色最知名的特質之一<ref>{{cite web|title=Londo Mollari on ‘Babylon 5’ ‘Memba Him?!|publisher=The Armenian Reporter|author=Jasyson|date=2020-05-22|url=https://www.reporter.am/londo-mollari-on-babylon-5-memba-him/|accessdate=2020-07-22|archive-date=2020-07-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200722105826/https://www.reporter.am/londo-mollari-on-babylon-5-memba-him/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=Babylon 5 redefined TV science fiction, so why isn’t it better known?|publisher=The A.V. Club|author=Rowan Kaiser|date=2012-11-07|url=https://tv.avclub.com/babylon-5-redefined-tv-science-fiction-so-why-isn-t-it-1798234450|accessdate=2020-07-22|archive-date=2020-07-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200703232116/https://tv.avclub.com/babylon-5-redefined-tv-science-fiction-so-why-isn-t-it-1798234450|dead-url=no}}</ref>。朱拉西科飾演的角色誇張、幽默、驕傲，有評論員指出這個髮型和角色的特質相符<ref>{{cite web|title=What the cast of Babylon 5 is doing today|author=Matthew Jackson|date=2020-02-27|publisher=Looper|url=https://www.looper.com/191120/what-the-cast-of-babylon-5-is-doing-today/|accessdate=2020-07-22|archive-date=2020-07-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200722070311/https://www.looper.com/191120/what-the-cast-of-babylon-5-is-doing-today/|dead-url=no}}</ref>，也有人一眼看到此造型就被影集吸引<ref>{{cite web|title=Upset of upsets, Babylon 5 ekes out past Battlestar Galactica|date=2020-03-13|author=Chad Porto|publisher=Redshirt Always Die|url=https://redshirtsalwaysdie.com/2020/03/13/babylon-5-eeks-battlestar-galactica/|accessdate=2020-07-22|archive-date=2020-07-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200722073748/https://redshirtsalwaysdie.com/2020/03/13/babylon-5-eeks-battlestar-galactica/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

在劇集中飾演另一位聖陶利角色的演員{{le|史蒂芬·佛斯特 (演員)|Stephen Furst|史蒂芬·佛斯特}}被錄用的原因也和聖陶利髮型有關。在[[試鏡|試鏡]]當天，佛斯特注意到其他來應徵的演員都做了此造形，但他因為遲到而沒有準備，他急忙到廁所試圖用[[肥皂|肥皂]]把自己的頭髮做成聖陶利髮型，卻讓肥皂沾到了眼睛。他還來不及處理好就被叫上場，他哭著向製作人解釋和道歉，製作人發覺他慌忙解釋的樣子正好就像劇中的角色，於是當場錄用他。<ref>{{cite web|title=What Happened to Stephen Furst?|publisher=Gazette Review|author=Barry W Stanton|date=2018-01-05|url=https://gazettereview.com/2018/01/what-happened-to-stephen-furst/|accessdate=2020-07-22|archive-date=2019-04-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190411051139/https://gazettereview.com/2018/01/what-happened-to-stephen-furst/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=18 Secrets Behind Babylon 5 Even Die-Hard Fans Don't Know|publisher=Screen Rant|author=Matt Morrison|date=2018-01-12|url=https://screenrant.com/babylon-5-dark-secrets-trivia-facts/|accessdate=2020-07-22|archive-date=2020-07-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200722070305/https://screenrant.com/babylon-5-dark-secrets-trivia-facts/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

==真實人物==
電視節目《[[遠古外星人|遠古外星人]]》的主持人[[喬治歐·托卡洛斯|喬治歐·托卡洛斯]]有類似的髮型，常被不知道他名字的人稱為「那個頭髮特別的人」（the hair guy）<ref>{{cite news|title=I want to believe: Meet the hair guy from “Ancient Aliens”|author=Don Jaucian|date=2016-08-26|publisher=CNN Philippines|url=https://cnnphilippines.com/life/entertainment/television/2016/08/26/ancient-aliens-giorgio-tsoukalos-interview.html|accessdate=2020-07-22|archive-date=2019-12-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191222153214/https://cnnphilippines.com/life/entertainment/television/2016/08/26/ancient-aliens-giorgio-tsoukalos-interview.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。他的這個髮型常被用在[[網路迷因|網路迷因]]中<ref>{{cite news|title=Aliens created God before leaving Earth, hair meme TV guy claims|date=2018-06-06|publisher=Metro|url=https://metro.co.uk/2018/06/06/aliens-created-god-leaving-earth-hair-meme-tv-guy-claims-7609793/|accessdate=2020-07-22|archive-date=2020-07-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200722183544/https://metro.co.uk/2018/06/06/aliens-created-god-leaving-earth-hair-meme-tv-guy-claims-7609793/|dead-url=no}}</ref>，包括一些迷因拿他和聖陶利人作比較<ref>{{cite web|title=Giorgio "Aliens" Tsoukalos Totally Looks Like Londo Mollari (Babylon 5)|publisher=Cheezburger|url=https://cheezburger.com/5258468352/giorgio-aliens-tsoukalos-totally-looks-like-londo-mollari-babylon-5|accessdate=2020-07-22|archive-date=2020-07-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200722102730/https://cheezburger.com/5258468352/giorgio-aliens-tsoukalos-totally-looks-like-londo-mollari-babylon-5|dead-url=no}}</ref>。在2010年[[臉書|臉書]]上甚至成立了以他的頭髮為主題的粉絲頁<ref>https://www.facebook.com/pg/GiorgioA.TsoukalosHair</ref>。雖然他的髮型看似雜亂，但其實大量使用[[髮膠|髮膠]]，是刻意維持的成果<ref>{{cite web|title=TV show host believes in aliens|date=2016-08-22|author=Yip Wai Yee|publisher=Straits Times|url=https://www.straitstimes.com/lifestyle/entertainment/tv-show-host-believes-in-aliens|accessdate=2020-07-22|archive-date=2020-07-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200722073730/https://www.straitstimes.com/lifestyle/entertainment/tv-show-host-believes-in-aliens|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

[[金正恩|金正恩]]向上梳高的髮型也曾被拿來與聖陶利人比較<ref>{{cite web|title=Kim Jong Un gets a Babylon 5 Centauri hair-do|publisher=Boing Boing|url=https://boingboing.net/2015/02/20/dear-leader-gets-a-babylon-5.html|accessdate=2020-07-22|archive-date=2020-06-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200624163501/https://boingboing.net/2015/02/20/dear-leader-gets-a-babylon-5.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|title=Kim Jong Un, Leader of North Korea, Debuts New Haircut and Trimmed Eyebrows|author=Corinne Heller|date=2015-02-20|publisher=E! Online|url=https://www.eonline.com/news/627556/kim-jong-un-leader-of-north-korea-debuts-new-haircut-and-trimmed-eyebrows-mdash-see-the-photos|accessdate=2020-07-22|archive-date=2020-07-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200722103825/https://www.eonline.com/news/627556/kim-jong-un-leader-of-north-korea-debuts-new-haircut-and-trimmed-eyebrows-mdash-see-the-photos|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

